FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [b].[Id], [b].[BuyerId], [b].[InsertTime], [b].[IsRemoved], [b].[RemoveTime], [b].[UpdateTime]

    WHERE ([b].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([b].[BuyerId] = @__userId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[UnitPrice], [b0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[AppType], [t0].[FirstRegisterDate], [t0].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [t0].[FirstRegisterUserId], [t0].[Fpid], [t0].[Guid], [t0].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [t0].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [t0].[LanguageId], [t0].[Month1], [t0].[OrderView], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [t0].[PrdBarCode], [t0].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdCode], [t0].[PrdColorId], [t0].[PrdCommissionDisable], [t0].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [t0].[PrdCrmId], [t0].[PrdDescription], [t0].[PrdDesign], [t0].[PrdFirstBarcode], [t0].[PrdFirstSerial], [t0].[PrdGroupId], [t0].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [t0].[PrdInactiveInSale], [t0].[PrdLatinName], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [t0].[PrdMaxQty], [t0].[PrdMinQty], [t0].[PrdModel], [t0].[PrdName], [t0].[PrdPrice], [t0].[PrdSecondBarcode], [t0].[PrdSecondSerial], [t0].[PrdShpcode], [t0].[PrdShpdescription], [t0].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [t0].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [t0].[PrdShpisActive], [t0].[PrdShpmodel], [t0].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [t0].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [t0].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [t0].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [t0].[PrdShptitle], [t0].[PrdSize], [t0].[PrdSleepDay], [t0].[PrdThirdBarcode], [t0].[PrdThirdSerial], [t0].[PrdType], [t0].[PrdUnitId], [t0].[RegisterDate], [t0].[RegisterDatePersian], [t0].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [t0].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [t0].[UserId]
    FROM [BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime], [p].[IsRemoved], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime], [p].[UpdateTime], [p].[UserId]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t0] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[UnitPrice], [b0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[AppType], [t0].[FirstRegisterDate], [t0].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [t0].[FirstRegisterUserId], [t0].[Fpid], [t0].[Guid], [t0].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [t0].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [t0].[LanguageId], [t0].[Month1], [t0].[OrderView], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [t0].[PrdBarCode], [t0].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdCode], [t0].[PrdColorId], [t0].[PrdCommissionDisable], [t0].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [t0].[PrdCrmId], [t0].[PrdDescription], [t0].[PrdDesign], [t0].[PrdFirstBarcode], [t0].[PrdFirstSerial], [t0].[PrdGroupId], [t0].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [t0].[PrdInactiveInSale], [t0].[PrdLatinName], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [t0].[PrdMaxQty], [t0].[PrdMinQty], [t0].[PrdModel], [t0].[PrdName], [t0].[PrdPrice], [t0].[PrdSecondBarcode], [t0].[PrdSecondSerial], [t0].[PrdShpcode], [t0].[PrdShpdescription], [t0].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [t0].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [t0].[PrdShpisActive], [t0].[PrdShpmodel], [t0].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [t0].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [t0].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [t0].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [t0].[PrdShptitle], [t0].[PrdSize], [t0].[PrdSleepDay], [t0].[PrdThirdBarcode], [t0].[PrdThirdSerial], [t0].[PrdType], [t0].[PrdUnitId], [t0].[RegisterDate], [t0].[RegisterDatePersian], [t0].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [t0].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [t0].[UserId]
    FROM [BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime], [p].[IsRemoved], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime], [p].[UpdateTime], [p].[UserId]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t0] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

        SELECT [w0].[SGName], 1 AS [c], [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] ORDER BY [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID]) AS [row]
        FROM [WSProductSecondGroup] AS [w0]
    ) AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [w].[PrdGroupID] = [t0].[PrdSecondGroupID]
ORDER BY [w].[ProductID] DESC" (0723d8ff)

        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime], [p].[IsRemoved], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime], [p].[UpdateTime], [p].[UserId]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t0] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[UnitPrice], [b0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[AppType], [t0].[FirstRegisterDate], [t0].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [t0].[FirstRegisterUserId], [t0].[Fpid], [t0].[Guid], [t0].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [t0].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [t0].[LanguageId], [t0].[Month1], [t0].[OrderView], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [t0].[PrdBarCode], [t0].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdCode], [t0].[PrdColorId], [t0].[PrdCommissionDisable], [t0].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [t0].[PrdCrmId], [t0].[PrdDescription], [t0].[PrdDesign], [t0].[PrdFirstBarcode], [t0].[PrdFirstSerial], [t0].[PrdGroupId], [t0].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [t0].[PrdInactiveInSale], [t0].[PrdLatinName], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [t0].[PrdMaxQty], [t0].[PrdMinQty], [t0].[PrdModel], [t0].[PrdName], [t0].[PrdPrice], [t0].[PrdSecondBarcode], [t0].[PrdSecondSerial], [t0].[PrdShpcode], [t0].[PrdShpdescription], [t0].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [t0].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [t0].[PrdShpisActive], [t0].[PrdShpmodel], [t0].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [t0].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [t0].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [t0].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [t0].[PrdShptitle], [t0].[PrdSize], [t0].[PrdSleepDay], [t0].[PrdThirdBarcode], [t0].[PrdThirdSerial], [t0].[PrdType], [t0].[PrdUnitId], [t0].[RegisterDate], [t0].[RegisterDatePersian], [t0].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [t0].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [t0].[UserId]
    FROM [BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime], [p].[IsRemoved], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime], [p].[UpdateTime], [p].[UserId]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t0] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[UnitPrice], [b0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[AppType], [t0].[FirstRegisterDate], [t0].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [t0].[FirstRegisterUserId], [t0].[Fpid], [t0].[Guid], [t0].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [t0].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [t0].[LanguageId], [t0].[Month1], [t0].[OrderView], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [t0].[PrdBarCode], [t0].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdCode], [t0].[PrdColorId], [t0].[PrdCommissionDisable], [t0].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [t0].[PrdCrmId], [t0].[PrdDescription], [t0].[PrdDesign], [t0].[PrdFirstBarcode], [t0].[PrdFirstSerial], [t0].[PrdGroupId], [t0].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [t0].[PrdInactiveInSale], [t0].[PrdLatinName], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [t0].[PrdMaxQty], [t0].[PrdMinQty], [t0].[PrdModel], [t0].[PrdName], [t0].[PrdPrice], [t0].[PrdSecondBarcode], [t0].[PrdSecondSerial], [t0].[PrdShpcode], [t0].[PrdShpdescription], [t0].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [t0].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [t0].[PrdShpisActive], [t0].[PrdShpmodel], [t0].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [t0].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [t0].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [t0].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [t0].[PrdShptitle], [t0].[PrdSize], [t0].[PrdSleepDay], [t0].[PrdThirdBarcode], [t0].[PrdThirdSerial], [t0].[PrdType], [t0].[PrdUnitId], [t0].[RegisterDate], [t0].[RegisterDatePersian], [t0].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [t0].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [t0].[UserId]
    FROM [BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime], [p].[IsRemoved], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime], [p].[UpdateTime], [p].[UserId]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t0] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

    WHERE ([b].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([b].[BuyerId] = @__userId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[UnitPrice], [b0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[AppType], [t0].[FirstRegisterDate], [t0].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [t0].[FirstRegisterUserId], [t0].[Fpid], [t0].[Guid], [t0].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [t0].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [t0].[LanguageId], [t0].[Month1], [t0].[OrderView], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [t0].[PrdBarCode], [t0].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdCode], [t0].[PrdColorId], [t0].[PrdCommissionDisable], [t0].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [t0].[PrdCrmId], [t0].[PrdDescription], [t0].[PrdDesign], [t0].[PrdFirstBarcode], [t0].[PrdFirstSerial], [t0].[PrdGroupId], [t0].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [t0].[PrdInactiveInSale], [t0].[PrdLatinName], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [t0].[PrdMaxQty], [t0].[PrdMinQty], [t0].[PrdModel], [t0].[PrdName], [t0].[PrdPrice], [t0].[PrdSecondBarcode], [t0].[PrdSecondSerial], [t0].[PrdShpcode], [t0].[PrdShpdescription], [t0].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [t0].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [t0].[PrdShpisActive], [t0].[PrdShpmodel], [t0].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [t0].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [t0].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [t0].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [t0].[PrdShptitle], [t0].[PrdSize], [t0].[PrdSleepDay], [t0].[PrdThirdBarcode], [t0].[PrdThirdSerial], [t0].[PrdType], [t0].[PrdUnitId], [t0].[RegisterDate], [t0].[RegisterDatePersian], [t0].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [t0].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [t0].[UserId]
    FROM [BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime], [p].[IsRemoved], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime], [p].[UpdateTime], [p].[UserId]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t0] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[UnitPrice], [b0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[AppType], [t0].[FirstRegisterDate], [t0].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [t0].[FirstRegisterUserId], [t0].[Fpid], [t0].[Guid], [t0].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [t0].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [t0].[LanguageId], [t0].[Month1], [t0].[OrderView], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [t0].[PrdBarCode], [t0].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdCode], [t0].[PrdColorId], [t0].[PrdCommissionDisable], [t0].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [t0].[PrdCrmId], [t0].[PrdDescription], [t0].[PrdDesign], [t0].[PrdFirstBarcode], [t0].[PrdFirstSerial], [t0].[PrdGroupId], [t0].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [t0].[PrdInactiveInSale], [t0].[PrdLatinName], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [t0].[PrdMaxQty], [t0].[PrdMinQty], [t0].[PrdModel], [t0].[PrdName], [t0].[PrdPrice], [t0].[PrdSecondBarcode], [t0].[PrdSecondSerial], [t0].[PrdShpcode], [t0].[PrdShpdescription], [t0].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [t0].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [t0].[PrdShpisActive], [t0].[PrdShpmodel], [t0].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [t0].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [t0].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [t0].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [t0].[PrdShptitle], [t0].[PrdSize], [t0].[PrdSleepDay], [t0].[PrdThirdBarcode], [t0].[PrdThirdSerial], [t0].[PrdType], [t0].[PrdUnitId], [t0].[RegisterDate], [t0].[RegisterDatePersian], [t0].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [t0].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [t0].[UserId]
    FROM [BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime], [p].[IsRemoved], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime], [p].[UpdateTime], [p].[UserId]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t0] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)
